'''西绪福斯山脉'''(Sisyphi Montes)[[火星|火星]]西绪福斯高原上的一座山脉，该山脉各处已呈现出不同程度侵蚀<ref name="Sisyphi Montes DD">{{cite web|title=Sisyphi Montes|url=http://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/polar2006/pdf/8066.pdf|accessdate=17 November 2012|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303212932/http://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/polar2006/pdf/8066.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，它直径约{{convert|200|km|mi|0}}，其名称取自一[[火星反照率特征列表|古典反照率名]]，1985年被[[国际天文联合会|国际天文联合会]]正式接受<ref name="Sisyphi Montes IAU">{{cite web|title=Sisyphi Montes|url=http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/5580|publisher=IAU|accessdate=17 November 2012|archive-date=2018-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180502212301/https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/5580|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Grego2012">{{cite book|author=Peter Grego|title=Mars and How to Observe It|url=https://archive.org/details/marshowtoobserve0000greg|url-access=registration|accessdate=17 November 2012|date=1 June 2012|publisher=Springer|isbn=978-1-4614-2302-7|pages=[https://archive.org/details/marshowtoobserve0000greg/page/135 135]–}}</ref>。该古典名字来源于[[希腊神话|希腊神话]]中的[[西西弗斯|西绪福斯]]神话，科林斯国王西绪福斯因欺骗诸神而在地狱里受罚，他必须将一块沉重的花岗岩推上一座山项，但每当他推至山顶时，石头又会滚落下来，他不得不重新开始，如此周而复始，永无止境<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.britannica.com/topic/Sisyphus |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-11-24 |archive-date=2021-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514010944/https://www.britannica.com/topic/Sisyphus |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由于该区域范围分布有许多山脉，因此，西绪福斯山脉使用了复数形式(Montes)<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://groups.google.com/forum/#!topic/alt.language.latin/Sh87u3lONbk |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-11-24 |archive-date=2019-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207213542/https://groups.google.com/forum/#!topic/alt.language.latin/Sh87u3lONbk |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

西绪福斯山脉坐落在[[南海区|南海区]]，介于阿耳古瑞和希腊撞击盆地之间<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://cosmochemistry-papers.com/2018/04/24/mineralogic-evidence-for-subglacial-volcanism-in-the-sisyphi-montes-region-of-mars/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-11-24 |archive-date=2018-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180626054854/https://cosmochemistry-papers.com/2018/04/24/mineralogic-evidence-for-subglacial-volcanism-in-the-sisyphi-montes-region-of-mars/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

