==冰原==
部分研究人员认为，南海区覆盖着一层大冰原<ref>Cassanelli, J. and J. Head.  2015.  Firn densification in a Late Noachian "icy highlands" Mars: implications for ice sheet evolution and thermal response.  Icarus:  253, 243-255.</ref><ref>Fastook, J. and J. Head.  2015.  Glaciation in the Late Noachian Icy highlands:  ice accumulation, distribution, flow rates, basal melting, and top-down melting rates and patterns.  Planet. Space Sci.  106, 82-98.</ref><ref>Smellie, J., B. Edwards. 2016. Glaciovolcanism on Earth and Mars. Cambridge University Press.</ref>，而西绪福斯山脉大约由100座穹丘状结构组成，类似地球上在冰原下喷发的火山<ref>Campbell, A., et al.  2016.  Morphology of Possible Subglacial Volcanoes in the Sysphi Montes Region of Mars. 47, 1554</ref>，相同的形状出现在[[冰岛|冰岛]]。这些圆顶距离现在的冰原非常远(1600公里)，现在的冰原只有350公里宽，而在过去则要大得多，且能容纳更多的水<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://crism.jhuapl.edu/newscenter/articles/20160503.php |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-11-24 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126090309/http://crism.jhuapl.edu/newscenter/articles/20160503.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 

[[火星专用小型侦察影像频谱仪|火星专用小型侦察影像频谱仪]]测量检测到火山在冰原下喷发时所形成的矿物质，发现的一些矿物有[[粘土|粘土]]、[[硫酸盐|硫酸盐]]、氧化铁和[[沸石|沸石]]，
这种组合通常称为[[橙玄玻璃|橙玄玻璃]]<ref>Ackiss, E., et al.  2016.  MINERALOGICAL EVIDENCE FOR SUBGLACIAL VOLCANOES IN THE SISYPHI MONTES REGION OF MARS. Sixth Mars Polar Science Conference (2016) 6086.pd</ref><ref>Ackiss, S., et al.  2018.  Mineralogic evidence for subglacial volcanism in the Sisyphi Montes region of Mars.  Icarus:  311:  357-370.</ref>。当火山在冰原下喷发时，会产生大量的温水，火星冰层下大量的温水可以为生命提供合适的生存场所，这样的环境也有利于化石的保存<ref>Cousins, C. and I. Crawford.  2011.  Volcano-ice interaction as a microbial Habitat on Earth and Mars.  Astrobiology:  11, 695-710.</ref>。

